      "role": "user",
      "content": "i was just sitting here looking out the window at this city and realized i don't think anyone here even knows i exist. like if i just stopped showing up to my cafe or stopped replying to texts, it would probably take weeks for anyone to notice. it’s weird how you can be surrounded by millions of people and just be totally invisible.",
